A Nigerian woman has been deported by the government of the UEA for traveling with the new Nigerian passport. A Nigerian woman has been deported for traveling with the new Nigerian passport because the Dubai government hasn’t been notified of the change by the Nigerian government. The woman identified as Bilikis shared her ordeal on social media. In a screenshot the sister of the said lady sent to Instablog9ja, she narrated how the Nigerian embassy couldn’t help them despite the N333k flight ticket fee they wasted. Watch the video: Lady deported for traveling with the new Nigerian passport because the Dubai government hasn’t been notified of the change. [Swipe] A post shared by  Instablog9ja (@instablog9ja) on Aug 21, 2019 at 2:58am PDT Source